dan dua mayat orang Romania di perahu.

498
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,159
Jadi kita harus apa?

499
00:36:28,679 --> 00:36:29,760
Oke.

500
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,719
Berlabuh di depan tanjakan.

501
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:35,000
