kita keluarkan perahunya dari air.

502
00:36:35,079 --> 00:36:37,000
Seharusnya tak lebih dari lima menit.

503
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,159
Kaki sialan!

504
00:36:47,119 --> 00:36:48,320
Bagus. Ayo pergi.

505
00:37:03,639 --> 00:37:06,079
Mungkin kita beruntung.
Ini seperti kota hantu.

506
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,639
Sial!

507
00:37:15,719 --> 00:37:17,480
Tak mungkin jadi begini!

508
00:37:17,559 --> 00:37:18,519
Aku harus bagaimana?

509
00:37:21,239 --> 00:37:24,159
Kau harus terus maju. Kami harus lewat!

510
00:37:24,239 --> 00:37:26,679
Tidak. Permisi. Benar, tolong minggir.

511
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,280
Terus jalan.

512
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:30,159
Zoe, bunyikan klakson.

513
00:37:30,239 --> 00:37:32,440
- Maaf. Bisa kau menyingkir?
- Ayo jalan. Ayo!

514
00:37:32,519 --> 00:37:33,920
Maaf. Tolong minggir!

515
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,320
Dengar, kami salah, oke?

516
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:41,159
Ayo... Maaf. Oke!

517
00:37:41,559 --> 00:37:44,239
Tolonglah! Sebentar!

518
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:48,320
Berengsek. Ini benar-benar mimpi buruk.

519
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,480
Kami memang salah, ya!

520
00:37:49,559 --> 00:37:51,280
Kami minta maaf, ya?

521
00:37:52,199 --> 00:37:54,400
Tidak, berhenti.

522
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:56,119
Ada anak naik ke perahu!

523
00:37:58,519 --> 00:37:59,440
Hei!

524
00:38:00,039 --> 00:38:03,840
Tidak. Keluar dari perahunya.
Keluar. Berikan itu.

525
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,719
Sial!

526
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:07,599
Kena kau!

527
00:38:07,679 --> 00:38:08,519
Enyahlah!

528
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:16,599
Sial!

529
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:22,679
Marcus, kau kenapa? yang terjadi?

530
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:24,480
Kau tak apa?

531
00:38:24,559 --> 00:38:26,360
- Pergi dari sini.
- Sial!

532
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,480
Aku tak bisa pergi.

533
00:38:27,559 --> 00:38:29,760
Pergilah! Sekarang!

534
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:30,760
Tolong!

535
00:38:35,079 --> 00:38:37,159
Astaga. Jangan begini lagi.

536
00:38:39,599 --> 00:38:40,719
Tolong!

537
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:43,920
Tidak, koplingnya rusak.
Kau harus tetap di gigi dua!

538
00:38:44,719 --> 00:38:45,840
Kau baik-baik saja?

539
00:38:46,239 --> 00:38:47,199
Enyah sana!

540
00:38:47,679 --> 00:38:48,760
Sialan!

541
00:39:41,119 --> 00:39:42,039
Sial!

542
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,280
Sial!

